<i>noun</i>: 도량 [도ː량] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도량 [도ː량]</dt><br>
<dd>1. generosity; broad-mindedness</dd><br>
<dd>너그럽게 받아들이고 깊게 이해할 수 있는 마음과 생각.</dd><br>
<dd>State of mind or thinking that can readily accept and deeply understand others.</dd><br>
<dd>2. calculation; measurement</dd><br>
<dd>길이, 부피, 무게 등을 재서 사물의 양을 헤아림.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of calculating the amount of something by measuring its length, volume, weight, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>